This avoids needing to use ```getattr()``` at all. Make sure that in your mapping dictionary you do not have parenthesis on the methods (ex. ```{&#39;Method 1&#39;: self.method_one()...```). If you do then ```chosen_method``` will equal whatever that method returns.

